                <h4 data-uuid="6e8554f6797245b8a3c1eb368a323146">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="4be7db3893df4d23858438915efb4a65">The Japanese continued advancing
                    across the Pacific in 1942.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="8b778c27304c4d0e9b18ba0b4288a0f3">Japan Advances</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="c94a40877b764c9196ccf7b5a31402bd"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
